This consortium, called "Énergie gérance," was in 2004 as part of the decision-making by Hydro-Québec, the private sector their responsibility, this important hydroelectric project a sum of $5 billion.
At the beginning of 2005 ergatterte the consortium "Énergie gérance" the lucrative contract without a public tender.
