She said that it "is the least" that the PQ apologize.
The model of the consortium is common practice in the world.
It is usually a time such a temporary alliance that it two or more companies their expertise on a requirement for a tender for a complex project.
The project "East Main" has a high level of complexity regarding his work from level.
The construction techniques is under way and should be established until 2012.
However, the Treaty was awarded without competition had taken place; it had already given negotiations.
