Rachsüchtige hackers and emsige spies
The affair WikiLeaks has a twofold significance.
On one hand, it proved to be an obvious scandal dictator, a scandal, only a scandal in Sinner hypocrisy is the Beziehunge between states, the public and the press.
On the other side announces it profound changes at international level, and is dominated by regression a foretaste of the future.
But we are going in the right order.
The first aspect of WikiLeaks is the confirmation of the fact that every Act (prepared by a secret service any nation) exclusively from newspaper cuttings.
The "extraordinary" American revelations about the sexual habits of Berlusconi's throw anything further than what for months as each anyway to read any Journal (except those whose owners Berlusconi), and the frightening karikaturierte profile Gaddafi's offered Kabarettkünstlern had fuel for a long time for their Sketche.
The principle of the secret dossier should only be already known news is essential for the dynamism of the secret services, and not just in this century.
If you go to a library, esotherischen publications, you will see that every plant (on the grail, the mystery of Rennes-le-Chateau Templer or the Rosenkreuzler) repeatedly exactly what has been written already in previous works.
This is not, therefore, that the author occult texts alone (still so that he does not know where news about the non-exist to find), but because those who devote to Okkultismus in nothing other than what they already know and confirmed what they have learned.
This is also the success mechanism of Dan Brown.
Also the secret files.
The informant is lazy and lazy (or limited spirit) is also the head of the secret service (for example, it could otherwise be whatever editor in Libération), the only true considers what he acknowledges.
The Top Secret information on Berlusconi, the American Embassy in Rome sent the Staatsdezernat were the same as those who already Newsweek published the week before.
So why was such a fuss about the revelations of this dossier?
On one side suggests that any educated person already know and that the messages - at least since the end of the Second World War, and since then the Government can call each other or a plane, in order to make dinner - have lost their diplomatic role and, with the exception of a couple of small have changed.
Any Ermittlungsfilmen viewers know this very well, and it is not for hypocrisy that acting to ignore it.
However, the fact to repeat it publicly, violates the task of hypocrisy and serves to American diplomacy in a bad light.
In second place: The idea that an x-random hacker intelligence secrets can tap into the most powerful country in the world, is the most significant blow to the prestige of the Staatsdezernats.
In addition, rather than victims, the scandal the "Executioner" in trouble.
But we are the profound nature of what happened.
Previously, Orwell's time, all controlled power as a Big Brother pool, every gesture of his subjects.
Orwell's prophecy could have proved quite right since then where one can control thanks to the phone every movement, every transaction, visited the hotel, the elected motorway and so on; the citizens would total victims the eye of power.
But if we see what is happening today, even the secret Krypten power can no longer control of a Hackers escape, to be directed Kontrollgang listening to unilaterally and will circle shaped.
The power controlled every citizen, but every citizen, or at least the hackers - chosen as avenger by the citizen - the secrets of power in experience.
How can a power that is no longer able to protect their own secrets?
It is true, Georg Simmel has already said that a real secret is a hollow secret (and an empty secret can never be unveiled); it is also true that any knowledge about the nature of Berlusconi's or Merkel's essentially a secret is free of Geheimis, because it exposes the public sphere; but in the style of WikiLeaks reveal that the secrets of Hillary Clinton empty secrets were meant to deprive it of any power.
WikiLeaks has neither Sarkozy nor Merkel wronged but Clinton and Obama.
What will be the consequences of this injury, which has caused a big power?
It is obvious that the states in future no longer online information - that would be a reserved in the street corner angeklebten form.
But it is also clear that with the current technology in vain hope is confidential reports on telephone secret.
Nothing is easier than finding out whether and when a Head of state in a plane and one of his colleagues contacted.
How could in future private and only for certain ears certain relations?
I know very well that my prediction at the moment for science fiction and Roman prison sounds, but I am forced to imagine the government agents in secret way preoccupied on uncontrollable march routes shattering, their communications anywhere else than the mere memory of order and, moreover, the few written information they received in the footwear (verbergend.
The information would be stored in single copy in closed drawers: Basically the Spionageversuch of Watergate had less success, as WikiLeaks.
I had the opportunity to write that the technology as a cancer progresses, namely backwards.
A century after the wireless telecommunications Count revolutionised communications had reconstructed the Internet a Telegrafen with (telephone) line.
The (analogue) video had the film allows them a film band for broadband auszukundschaften by forward from behind spulen and all could reveal mysteries of the assembly, while the (digital) CDs, today nothing other than from chapter to chapter to jump in macro-portions.
With the high-speed trains travel within three hours by plane from Rome to Milan, while this including of switching requires three and a half hours.
It is therefore not return to the car and horse exceptionally, policy and communications technology.
A final observation.
In earlier times, the press to understand what secrets between the messages were forged.
Currently, there are the messages that confidential information from the press.
Climate France: How its financial promises nice talking
A year after the Copenhagen Treaty, it is time to examine compliance with the financing pledge quickly resolved (also called "fast start" or premature finance), which the developing countries.
And the rough French vulnerable to blandishments.
With the Copenhagen treaty the developing countries have committed to provide $30 billion between 2010 and 2012.
The EU has EUR 7.2 billion over three years, France 1.26 billion euros (i.e. 420 million per year).
At the opening of the COP16, the EU has pulled out all the stops in order to convince its partners from the fact their commitment regarding the fast-start financing: Detailgetreuer report their Member States, press conference, big-events, brochures distribution.
The operation is remarkable and transparency engenders around appreciated for their intrinsic value: The developing countries and the society would like to see all developed countries, the same thing at the same level of precision.
The EU announced EUR 2.2 billion in 2010 to have released what they on the right path to Respektbezollung commitment of 7.2 billion in 2012.
But if you look in detail, things are a little more complicated.
This money should be according to the Copenhagen treaty "new and additional" in order to ensure that an additional deployment, without detriment of public development aid.
Unfortunately, there is no consensus on what the "new and additional" means.
While the Commission had proposed a harmonisation, certain Member states, including France, to block the procedure.
Today everyone chooses The benchmark, which he considers the best.
The EU Commission has, for example, as a benchmark for those of 2009: The international funding are maintained, and 150 million in "fast start-up financing framework" over three years.
Other countries have similar standards, either on year or about conditions at the level of public development aid.
In return, France was of the opinion that the funding of all new projects "of the year 2010 are" new and additional ".
In other words, there is no guidelines on the spending of the previous year or at the global level of public development aid.
Specifically, the sum total of French support for developing countries remain stable (or decline) - France, his commitment to the "new and additional funding."
Another crucial element is the breakdown in donations and loans.
There is still no rule, and everyone chooses his Rechenmodus.
Some, such as France, 1 borrowed €as being equivalent to €1 donated.
Obviously this is not acceptable that the effort is not comparable.
If the use of loans for certain profitable investment (often linked to the emission reduction projects based on the most effective technology) cannot be justified, it is deceptive to present the euro, as equivalent to a donated euro captured... should also be included only the cost of the loan for the capital donor country than commitment (i.e. the equivalent of an interest rate).
But France has nothing else in terms than the following consideration: it "respected" its commitment of EUR 420 million by 91.5% loan (389,8 million euros) and 8.5% donates) 36.1 million euros) - see the EU document to convince themselves.
France is the only land the EU that loans to a great extent.
Germany 46%, while Denmark, the Netherlands and Slovakia (among other things) their commitments to 100% with donations.
In other words, if the vast majority of the European Union spends €to fulfil their obligations, France just 10 cents and understands including a comparable efforts.
Fine Hokuspokus!
All in all, operates France in its fast-start financing with a double fraud: To part with a Weiterentwicklkung of action over the period and partly with the reality of financial support.
France manage to believe that 420 million "new and additional" has spent millions in accordance with its promise and saves EUR 36.1 million.
The manipulation of the Treasury (as it appears that it was Bercy has implemented the arbitrage) could entail a double negative impact; even EU internally (why the other Member states, with the donations, if there is enough to lend?) and then in the negotiations, because the developing countries is not completely deceived...
The chapter of premature funding only a small issue on relatively short time compared to the discussions on the climate.
But it could be too much in the massive machinery of the UNFCCC.
We hope that this will not be the case.
As always, it is essential to learn its lesson from this first year of early funding.
In the first instance France could be a change in its accounting for the years 2011 and 2012, and in a spirit of respect for his commitments and the counterbalancing justice with the other countries of the European Union.
But especially France could bring forward the discussions on the subject of long-term financing dispute (another key topic) and at the moment: You can escape the question of "Verrechenbarkeit" or the recording its loans.
France could change its position as progressive in terms of the issues to be as it is for other things.
The hope is based on the new environment minister Kosciusko-Morizet next week in Cancun will arrive.
A surprising announcement on the fast-start France and his vision of "Verrechenbarkeit" and the use of loans would increase the international confidence by nature, which is necessary for further discussions.
